**Query #3**

    -- 1. Date Difference (DATEDIFF)
    -- Days since order was placed
    
    SELECT 
        customer_name,
        order_date,
        DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), order_date) AS days_ago
    FROM Orders;

| customer_name | order_date | days_ago |
| ------------- | ---------- | -------- |
| Alice         | 2026-03-24 | 10       |
| Bob           | 2026-02-22 | 40       |
| Charlie       | 2026-03-29 | 5        |
| David         | 2026-03-14 | 20       |
| Eve           | 2026-02-02 | 60       |

